data.description: Welcome home to this big, beautiful, multi-level in Eldorado. Beautifully updated kitchen with soft close drawers and cabinet doors. Primary bedroom with separate access to professionally remodeled bathroom with dual sinks and light, bright finishes. 2,300 finished square feet with tons of room to hang-out. Massive family room with huge, brick fireplace and lots of space for big gatherings of family and friends with a walk-out patio door to spacious common ground. The covered patio is great for relaxing and cooking out. Three bedrooms upstairs with 3 "other" finished rooms in the basement. Two car garage and lots of storage.
